Changes in 1.30 Gamma 1
=======================

   @{b}*@{ub} fixed date problems AGAIN.

   @{b}*@{ub} fixed DLGAREAS in FFRS and FFRI.

   @{b}*@{ub} added support for CNet 2.60+

     Keywords:

     CNET219         CNet 2.19 to 2.59

     CNET            CNet 2.60 and up


@EndNode

