Changes in 2.3
==============

   @{b}*@{ub} New parameter for CNet.

   @{b}*@{ub} Use now CNET26x for version 2.60 to 2.69+.

   @{b}*@{ub} Use now CNET3xx for version 3.05c and i hope the future upgrade.

   @{b}*@{ub} Future version of FFRS:

     Resulting of bad support for ADS and SAN here, the upgrade will be
     available ONLY on my BBS and in Aminet (section comm/fido)

@EndNode

